<p>If one of the aforementioned conditions is met, and a data subject wishes to request the restriction of the processing of personal data stored by {PAGENAME}, he or she may at any time contact our Data Protection Officer or another employee of the controller. The Data Protection Officer of {PAGENAME} or another employee will arrange the restriction of the processing. </p>
